CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Yoshiharu Global Co is a Japanese restaurant operator. The company has one reportable segment, consisting of operating its stores. Yoshiharu serves the perfect, ideal ramen, as well as offers customers a wide variety of sushi, bento menu, and other favorite Japanese cuisines. It is owning and operating 6 restaurant stores with an additional 3 in development and 8 expected to open.
